membership:
ESF is a member of FAIB&#xd;
ESF is a partner of the EU-OSHA agency for their campaigns on occupational health and safety&#xd;
ESF is an active stakeholder in meetings of the EU commission (DG GROW - PPE directive)&#xd;
ESF is an active partner of the Coordination of the Notified Bodies in the field of PPE&#xd;
ESF is active within CEN-CENELEC standardisation (e.g. Secretary General is chair of the PPE sector forum)&#xd;
ESF works together with organisations such as ETSA, EURATEX, CEFIC, ESIG, FESI, ANEC, BUSINESS EUROPE, ... on specific issues

